---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";

const { nomargin } = Astro.props;
---

<div class="bg-custom-blue lg:col-span-5 pb-6 md:pb-10">
  <div class="pb-6 md:pb-10 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:ml-40 lg:mr-20">
    <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-6 md:mb-8 [text-wrap:balance] text-white font-bold leading-tight">
      Is your deployment pipeline duct-taped together?
    </h3>
    <ul class="mt-4 md:mt-6 space-y-3 md:space-y-5 text-left">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-custom-gray">
        <Icon name="ph:circle-fill" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 min-w-4 min-h-4 md:min-w-5 md:min-h-5 mt-1" />
        <span class="text-base md:text-xl">Manual scripts with no rollback strategy</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-custom-gray">
        <Icon name="ph:circle-fill" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 min-w-4 min-h-4 md:min-w-5 md:min-h-5 mt-1" />
        <span class="text-base md:text-xl">No traffic shifting — updates still break prod</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-custom-gray">
        <Icon name="ph:circle-fill" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 min-w-4 min-h-4 md:min-w-5 md:min-h-5 mt-1" />
        <span class="text-base md:text-xl">Ops teams scrambling during incidents</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-custom-gray">
        <Icon name="ph:circle-fill" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 min-w-4 min-h-4 md:min-w-5 md:min-h-5 mt-1" />
        <span class="text-base md:text-xl">Zero visibility into what was deployed and why</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-custom-gray">
        <Icon name="ph:circle-fill" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 min-w-4 min-h-4 md:min-w-5 md:min-h-5 mt-1" />
        <span class="text-base md:text-xl">No Git traceability — configs live outside version control</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="italic text-lg md:text-2xl border-l-4 border-teal-custom pl-2 mt-6 md:mt-8 text-white leading-relaxed">You shouldn't be scared to deploy on a Friday.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 md:mt-20 pb-6 md:pb-10 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:ml-40 lg:mr-40">
    <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-6 md:mb-8 [text-wrap:balance] text-white font-bold leading-tight">
      Gitmoxi makes your deploys as safe and simple as a Git commit
    </h3>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-10 mt-6 md:mt-8">
      <div class="bg-gray-200 rounded-xl p-4 md:p-5">
        <div class="font-bold pb-2 md:pb-3 text-lg md:text-xl">1. Git-Powered Deployments</div>
        <p class="text-base md:text-xl leading-relaxed">Push a config file to Git. That's it. We handle deploy logic, CI/CD, and rollback.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-200 rounded-xl p-4 md:p-5">
        <div class="font-bold pb-2 md:pb-3 text-lg md:text-xl">2. Safe Deployment Strategies</div>
        <p class="text-base md:text-xl leading-relaxed">Blue/green, rolling, canary — with health checks and alarms. Breaks? We auto-revert.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-200 rounded-xl p-4 md:p-5 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="font-bold pb-2 md:pb-3 text-lg md:text-xl">3. Complete Audit Trail</div>
        <p class="text-base md:text-xl leading-relaxed">Every change is traceable to a commit, user, and timestamp. No more guesswork.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 md:mt-20 pb-6 md:pb-10 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:ml-40 lg:mr-40">
    <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-6 md:mb-8 [text-wrap:balance] text-white font-bold leading-tight">
      From chaos to confidence — here's what changes
    </h3>
    <ul class="mt-4 md:mt-6 space-y-3 md:space-y-5 text-left">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-custom-gray">
        <Icon name="lucide:check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-green-500 mt-1" />
        <span class="text-base md:text-xl">Zero-downtime Deploys</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-custom-gray">
        <Icon name="lucide:check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-green-500 mt-1" />
        <span class="text-base md:text-xl">Full Observability</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-custom-gray">
        <Icon name="lucide:check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-green-500 mt-1" />
        <span class="text-base md:text-xl">AI-Powered Troubleshooting</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-custom-gray">
        <Icon name="lucide:check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-green-500 mt-1" />
        <span class="text-base md:text-xl">Lower Cloud Spend</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-custom-gray">
        <Icon name="lucide:check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-green-500 mt-1" />
        <span class="text-base md:text-xl">Dev & Ops Move Faster</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>